@bluebill1049 Happens to me all too often.

Bummer... I changed NPM from `^6.1.2" to "^6.2.0" and it's still not working as expected...
1min demo video: https://share.getcloudapp.com/rRu7JPkQ

I have this setup:
```js
const { control, formState, handleSubmit, setValue, watch } = useForm( {
	mode: 'onBlur',
	reValidateMode: 'all',
} );
```

If there's a different set of args to send to useForm that _would_ make `formState.isValid` work as expected, please let me know.
